              "free_text": [
                "Fits to the measured (arbitrary units) yields at each",
                "angle were then performed. The standard angular",
                "distribution function W(theta) = a0[1 + a2P2(cos theta)",
                " + a4P4(cos theta) ], where P2 and P4 are Legendre",
